or: orange;\">「五大訴求，缺一不可」</span>。<br />\n方式可以係由下至上爭取、撼動政權 &mdash;<span style=\"color: violet;\"> 時代革命</span>。<br />\n亦唔排除係徹底推翻現有政權 &mdash; <span style=\"color: red;\">香港獨立</span>。<br />\n<br />\n所以我提議黎緊口號演變成以下三項為主軸。<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">「五大訴求，缺一不可」</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">「光復香港，時代革命」</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">「民主自決，香港獨立」</span></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T09:50:14.000Z","msg":"民族自決，你要民主自決同朱西迪主飽佢"},{"pid":"9be94e4bc5926a147e34df1c0b67ece6fc4d6d0b","tid":1682824,"uid":159428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T09:50:27.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"da37b9ca50892c4d1dc5513c7894ada4083bb7b3","tid":1682824,"uid":159428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T09:51:30.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"300f76de71712bc1a2ce65d2e443877b04aeec69","tid":1682824,"uid":292710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9be94e4bc5926a147e34df1c0b67ece6fc4d6d0b","tid":1682824,"uid":159428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T09:50:27.000Z","msg":"自推"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T09:51:32.000Z","msg":"唔要民主自決！<br />\n我要民族自決，香港獨立"},{"pid":"7d806379fc4a3670335c2f85ec450a70eefc26bb","tid":1682824,"uid":159428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"300f76de71712bc1a2ce65d2e443877b04aeec69","tid":1682824,"uid":292710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9be94e4bc5926a147e34df1c0b67ece6fc4d6d0b","tid":1682824,"uid":159428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T09:50:27.000Z","msg":"自推"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T09:51:32.000Z","msg":"唔要民主自決！<br />\n我要民族自決，香港獨立"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T09:55:04.000Z","msg":"其實我喺依點上冇執著 我提出只係因為見到Gphone DQ啲新聞<br />\n口號共識都要靠大家去討論"},{"pid":"8ff294dbd572fc1a19da579b769e4a0fd09e33c9","tid":1682824,"uid":287547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T09:57:38.000Z","msg":"營業模式:  <br />\n<br />\n<strong>根據手足經濟能力的不